text: Tumhi pahala ki jyancya manata vikara ahe te dhavata ja'una tyancyata misalatata ani mhanatata ki amhala bhaya vatate ki kadacita ase na vhave ki ekhade sankata amacyavara kosalave, phara sakya ahe ki allahane vijaya pradana karava kinva apalyakaduna an'ya ekhada phaisala karava maga tara he apalya manata lapavilelya gostibaddala khupa lajjita hotila
